<h1>Gamezone</h1>
<div id="gamezone" class="text-center">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2">
			<div class="card card-danger mb-3">
				<div class="card-block">
					<h4 class="card-title">
						<u><i class="fa fa-trophy"></i> Level 1</u>
						<br>
						Speed Speller
					</h4>
					<p class="card-text">
						Type the target word as fast as you can. See if you can beat
						your previous typing record and earn even more Linero each time
						you type the word.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="card card-danger mb-3">
				<div class="card-block">
					<h4 class="card-title">
						<u><i class="fa fa-trophy"></i> Level 2</u>
						<br>
						Jumbled Spelling
					</h4>
					<p class="card-text">
						The letters for the target word have been mixed up and it's up
						to you to correctly put them back together.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="card card-danger mb-3">
				<div class="card-block">
					<h4 class="card-title">
						<u><i class="fa fa-trophy"></i> Level 3</u>
						<br>
						Say It Right
					</h4>
					<p class="card-text">
						Hear the pronunciation for the target word and say it right
						yourself.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="card card-danger mb-3">
				<div class="card-block">
					<h4 class="card-title">
						<u><i class="fa fa-trophy"></i> Level 4</u>
						<br>
						Decisions, Decisions
					</h4>
					<p class="card-text">
						You have the power to make important choices in this Level -
						be careful with the decisions you make.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="card card-danger mb-3">
				<div class="card-block">
					<h4 class="card-title">
						<u><i class="fa fa-trophy"></i> Level 5</u>
						<br>
						Examples/Non-Examples
					</h4>
					<p class="card-text">
						Here you'll determine whether the given scenarios are a legit
						representation of the target word.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="card card-danger mb-3">
				<div class="card-block">
					<h4 class="card-title">
						<u><i class="fa fa-trophy"></i> Level 6</u>
						<br>
						Syns versus Ants
					</h4>
					<p class="card-text">
						Match the synonym and antonym pairs for the target word.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="card card-warning mb-3">
				<div class="card-block">
					<h4 class="card-title">
						<u><i class="fa fa-trophy"></i> Level 7</u>
						<br>
						Match 'Em All
					</h4>
					<p class="card-text">
						Description coming soon!
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="card card-warning mb-3">
				<div class="card-block">
					<h4 class="card-title">
						<u><i class="fa fa-trophy"></i> Level 8</u>
						<br>
						Jeopardy
					</h4>
					<p class="card-text">
						Earn lots of Linero by picking a category and amount and then
						answering the question correctly. Of course, if you answer
						incorrectly, then you'll lose Linero.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="card card-success mb-3">
				<div class="card-block">
					<h4 class="card-title">
						<u><i class="fa fa-trophy"></i> Level 9</u>
						<br>
						Sentence Stems
					</h4>
					<p class="card-text">
						In this Level, you'll meet us halfway by finishing the given
						sentences for the target word.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="card card-success mb-3">
				<div class="card-block">
					<h4 class="card-title">
						<u><i class="fa fa-trophy"></i> Level 10</u>
						<br>
						Word Relationships
					</h4>
					<p class="card-text">
						Some words can be more alike than you think! Determine how the
						given words can relate to each other.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="card card-success mb-3">
				<div class="card-block">
					<h4 class="card-title">
						<u><i class="fa fa-trophy"></i> Level 11</u>
						<br>
						Leksi Tale
					</h4>
					<p class="card-text">
						Unleash your creativity by creating a short story, poem, rap, etc.
						with at least three of your words. This can be real or fake so
						have fun with it.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="card card-success mb-3">
				<div class="card-block">
					<h4 class="card-title">
						<u><i class="fa fa-trophy"></i> Level 12</u>
						<br>
						Describe Me, Describe Me Not
					</h4>
					<p class="card-text">
						Hmmm...would you want to be described by the target word? In this
						Level, you'll briefly explain why.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="card card-success mb-3">
				<div class="card-block">
					<h4 class="card-title">
						<u>
							<i class="fa fa-trophy"></i> Level X <i class="fa fa-trophy"></i>
						</u>
						<br>
						In My Life
					</h4>
					<p class="card-text">
						Have you heard any of your words being used in the media, magazines,
						TV, social media, etc.? If so, come here to save that encounter and
						earn some serious Linero!
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="card card-outline-secondary mb-3">
				<div class="card-block">
					<i class="fa fa-plus-circle"></i> Suggest a New Level
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
